{"tid":1291512,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"南區連儂牆","createTime":"2019-07-07T02:28:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T13:33:44.000Z","uid":234679,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"15da326d540a739e896ed7e1ba40275a21338794","tid":1291512,"uid":234679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T02:28:09.000Z","msg":"大家好，我哋係南區民眾組織，宜家籌備喺香港仔搞連儂牆，目的係可以令市民關注到反送中行動，並且鼓勵以及為香港人打氣，希望大家會積極支持行動，為香港出一分力。無論你係支持行動又好，反對行動又好，都歡迎你黎以下地點寫低你哋嘅心聲❤️<br />\n<br />\n收集memo次序<br />\n7/7 東邨(MTR exit)+大街(MTR exit)(1730)<br />\n8/7 西邨(大快活對開)+海怡(MTR exitB)(1730)<br />\n9/7 華富(酒家巴士站)+華貴(巴士站)+置富(巴士總站)+田灣（ok便利店）(1730)<br />\n10/7 石排灣(扶手梯斑馬線)+香港仔(橋底)+黃竹坑(MTR天橋)(1730)<br />\n以上結束時間會視乎當日情況<br />\n<br />\n最終日期<br />\n11/7 香港仔橋底聚返(連儂牆)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FL1GeDU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFL1GeDU.jpg&h=127b3655&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5e3c718d9892cb32036d7fb0254d042f2d5b27f4","tid":1291512,"uid":34049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T02:29:19.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">我冇野講</code></pre>"},{"pid":"0e7d7bf5affcec361af31c157a5b1e1e40d0bccc","tid":1291512,"uid":234679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T02:31:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0d9cf67f5b0405c6b922405c46e42277003e6855","tid":1291512,"uid":234679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T02:33:01.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4efc4521fb3ce15de6dc23f1dbcb1fccaad2d600","tid":1291512,"uid":234679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T02:35:45.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"640b1b2facba3d07981b83632a3b7baae14cd573","tid":1291512,"uid":234679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T02:40:03.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5d88706832351cf32e148386c8fcb53cb30e3af1","tid":1291512,"uid":785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T02:43:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/